3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves training and optimizing a deep learning model for instance segmentation.
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses real-time instance segmentation, which could be relevant to robotics applications.
